"counter-reset:line-number 0\"><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div></div></div><h3 id=\"使用\" tabindex=\"-1\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#使用\"><span>使用</span></a></h3>\n<ol>\n<li>在终端运行bash命令，并等待debug</li>\n</ol>\n<img src=\"@source/blog/Vscode经验总结.assets/image-20250528121207875.png\" alt=\"image-20250528121207875\" style=\"zoom: 67%;\" />\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>打上断点，点击调试按钮<code v-pre>sh_file_debug</code>，开始debug</li>\n</ol>\n<img src=\"@source/blog/Vscode经验总结.assets/image-20250528121356382.png\" alt=\"image-20250528121356382\" style=\"zoom: 37%;\" />","tagOpen":"<template>","tagClose":"</template>"},"script":null,"scriptSetup":null,"scripts":[],"styles":[],"customBlocks":[]},"content":"## ssh免密连接设置\r\n\r\n服务器端：\r\n\r\n1. 用户目录权限为775\r\n\r\n2. 服务器的ssh配置\r\n\r\n```bash\r\nPubkeyAuthentication yes\r\nAuthorizedKeysFile      .ssh/authorized_keys\r\n```\r\n\r\n3. 在本机生成rsa私钥公钥。私钥放本地，公钥放服务器\r\n\r\n```bash\r\nssh-keygen -t rsa\r\n本地：\r\n- C:\\Users\\19124/.ssh/id_rsa\r\n- C:\\Users\\19124/.ssh/id_rsa.pub\r\n服务器：\r\n- 将公钥(.pub)传入服务器放入以下路径：~/.ssh/authorized_keys\r\n\r\n便捷代码：echo \"xxxx\" >> ~/.ssh/authorized_keys\r\n```\r\n\r\n4. vscode远程连接配置认证文件\r\n\r\n```bash\r\nIdentityFile ~/.ssh/authorized_keys\r\n```\r\n\r\n## 创建项目\r\n\r\n以每个项目为中心，各个项目隔离\r\n\r\n## 带参debug\r\n\r\n如何在vscode中顺滑的debug python文件？\r\n\r\n### 配置\r\n\r\n1. 安装依赖包：`pip install debugpy -U`\r\n2. 添加带参数的`launch.json`文件配置并选择`sh_file_debug`\r\n\r\n```json\r\n{\r\n    \"name\": \"sh_file_debug\",\r\n    \"type\": \"debugpy\",\r\n    \"request\": \"attach\",\r\n    \"connect\": {\r\n        \"host\": \"localhost\",\r\n        \"port\": 9501\r\n    }\r\n},\r\n```\r\n\r\n3. 在python代码前加上这句话\r\n\r\n```py\r\nimport debugpy\r\ntry:\r\n    # 5678 is the default attach port in the VS Code debug configurations. Unless a host and port are specified, host defaults to 127.0.0.1\r\n    debugpy.listen((\"localhost\", 9501))\r\n    print(\"Waiting for debugger attach\")\r\n    debugpy.wait_for_client()\r\nexcept Exception as e:\r\n    pass\r\n```\r\n\r\n### 使用\r\n\r\n1. 在终端运行bash命令，并等待debug\r\n\r\n<img src=\"./Vscode%E7%BB%8F%E9%AA%8C%E6%80%BB%E7%BB%93.assets/image-20250528121207875.png\" alt=\"image-20250528121207875\" style=\"zoom: 67%;\" />\r\n\r\n2. 打上断点，点击调试按钮`sh_file_debug`，开始debug\r\n\r\n<img src=\"./Vscode%E7%BB%8F%E9%AA%8C%E6%80%BB%E7%BB%93.assets/image-20250528121356382.png\" alt=\"image-20250528121356382\" style=\"zoom: 37%;\" />","excerpt":"","includedFiles":[],"tasklistId":0,"title":"","headers":[{"level":2,"title":"ssh免密连接设置","slug":"ssh免密连接设置","link":"#ssh免密连接设置","children":[]},{"level":2,"title":"创建项目","slug":"创建项目","link":"#创建项目","children":[]},{"level":2,"title":"带参debug","slug":"带参debug","link":"#带参debug","children":[{"level":3,"title":"配置","slug":"配置","link":"#配置","children":[]},{"level":3,"title":"使用","slug":"使用","link":"#使用","children":[]}]}]}}
